 <!-- How to calculate -->
 <section style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
 <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
 <h2 class="section-h2">How to find your life path number</h2>
 <p class="text-muted-text leading-relaxed mb-6">
 To find your life path number, reduce your full birth date to a single digit - or a master number. Write out your date of birth as three parts: month, day, and year. Reduce each to a single digit, add them together, and if the result is 11, 22, or 33, stop.
 </p>
 <div class="card-light p-6 mb-6">
 <div class="font-bold text-body-text mb-4 font-[family-name:var(--font-family-heading)]">
 Example: September 2, 1966
 </div>
 <div class="space-y-2 text-sm font-mono">
 <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
 <span class="text-violet font-bold w-16 shrink-0">Month:</span>
 <span class="text-muted-text">9 (September = 9)</span>
 </div>
 <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
 <span class="text-violet font-bold w-16 shrink-0">Day:</span>
 <span class="text-muted-text">2</span>
 </div>
 <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
 <span class="text-violet font-bold w-16 shrink-0">Year:</span>
 <span class="text-muted-text">1 + 9 + 6 + 6 = 22 ← master number, not reduced</span>
 </div>
 <div class="border-t border-border/40 pt-2 mt-2 flex items-center gap-2">
 <span class="text-gold font-bold w-16 shrink-0">Total:</span>
 <span class="text-body-text font-bold">9 + 2 + 22 = <span class="text-violet">33</span> ← master number, not reduced</span>
 </div>
 </div>
 <p class="text-xs text-muted-text mt-4">Birth date of Salma Hayek. The year 1966 reduces to 22, a master number, so we preserve it rather than reducing it further. This is what makes LP33 so rare: the year component must reduce to a master number, and the remaining components must sum to reach 33 exactly.</p>
 </div>
 <p class="text-muted-text leading-relaxed mb-4">
 The master number rule: if your final total is 11, 22, or 33, it stays as-is. If your total is 33 and you want to verify, 3+3=6 is the base energy - LP33 contains LP6, amplified and directed at a level of universal compassion.
 </p>
 <p class="text-muted-text leading-relaxed">
 Want step-by-step examples for every possible scenario?
 <a href="/learn/how-to-calculate-life-path-number/" class="text-violet hover:underline font-medium">Read the full calculation guide →</a>
 </p>
 </div>
 </section>

